 <p>We're not the cheapest room in Vernal, and we're not the most expensive. What we are is the best all-in value — the most amenities per dollar, with the convenience of a central location 0.6 miles from the airport and within easy driving distance of every major attraction in the Uintah Basin.</p>
 <ul class="feat-list">
